  <div> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},<br /> <br /> I hope all is well. Given the current circumstance, I wanted to reach out and assure you that Citron Hygiene is committed to supporting your business during these unprecedented times.<br /> <br /> Many of the businesses I work with have reached out asking for information on what increased hygiene measures should be taken into consideration for their facility. As we continue to minimize the spread, I thought I would share with you one of the key recommendations I am informing businesses of, which is <u><i>implementing a touch-free washroom</i></u>.<br /> <br /> Protecting your employees and customers is vital to your business, which is why it is important to have proactive hygiene measures in place to ensure future outbreaks do not happen. <b>Research has indicated that COVID-19 can survive on surfaces for up to 72 hours, making washrooms a place of risk to patrons and employees</b>. Additionally, washroom fixtures such as taps, toilets and sinks can house thousands of bacteria per square inch.&nbsp; Each time an individual touches a tap, sink or toilet in your washroom, they risk being exposed to viruses and bacteria and then tracking them throughout your facility.<br /> <br /> As it is almost impossible to ensure a washroom is properly cleaned and sanitized before each use, touch-free washroom fixtures provide a safe and effective alternative to minimize health risks. A washroom that has implemented touch-free fixtures can effectively eliminate the need for an individual to touch sanitary disposal units, sinks, hand dryers, soap and paper towel dispensers. These measures safeguard your employees and customers, keeping your facility healthy and hygienic.<br /> <br /> At Citron Hygiene, we realize the health risks users experience in the washroom and have a full range of solutions that <b>reduce surface-to-person contact</b>. For over 40 years, Citron Hygiene has helped businesses minimize hygiene risks in commercial facilities. I am confident our solutions will provide a safe alternative that your employees will recognize and appreciate.<br /> <br /> I would like to help your business create a back to work hygiene plan, to keep your employees and customers safe. I am available to meet virtually to further discuss the&nbsp;</span></span> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><a href="https://www.citronhygiene.com/solutions/washroom-hygiene/washroom-automation/">touch-free solutions</a>&nbsp;</span></span> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">we have for your washroom. Please do not hesitate to reach out if you have any questions, I look forward to hearing from you.<br /> <br /> Thank you,<br /> <br /> {{{Sender.Name}}}</span></span> 
   <br /> 
